{"tid":903074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(韓粉請入)馬英九高雄助選 站台又口誤:香港又老又窮","createTime":"2018-11-15T09:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T06:19:00.000Z","uid":1372,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c2fbe1c12faaf4a6394ee01047820bc70442bc","tid":903074,"uid":1372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"2018-11-15 14:00<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2613421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2613421&d=XciyCYDR5ar%2FqBRqMlYw9wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=84b937d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2613421&h=10046c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2613421</a><br />\n<br />\n馬英九今上午在國民黨市議員候選人邱于軒陪同下，前往高雄市大寮區仁愛<br />\n之家探視長輩，被仁愛之家董事長張雅玲問及 2年後是否再度參選總統，僅<br />\n回「謝謝關心」；不過馬英九在發表談話時，竟口誤表示「香港又老又窮」<br />\n，讓邱尷尬提醒，馬才錯愕回應「我剛剛說什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n馬英九在現場發表談話時，指出「韓國瑜也提到，香港是又老又窮」，一旁<br />\n邱于軒立刻提醒馬「是高雄」，馬當時錯愕回應「我剛剛說什麼？」，邱則<br />\n回：「你講成香港」馬隨後笑說「香港啊，香港也差不多，高雄又老又窮」<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1542271933.A.28F.html?fbclid=IwAR1ykpJqGIpfh4Px6QWbFBGRhgpXW2_6GhmynOSRTpAbjKv-RZfAI71I08U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1542271933.A.28F.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ykpJqGIpfh4Px6QWbFBGRhgpXW2_6GhmynOSRTpAbjKv-RZfAI71I08U&d=XciyCYDR5ar%2FqBRqMlYw9wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=409d0b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1542271933.A.28F.html?fbclid=IwAR1ykpJqGIpfh4Px6QWbFBGRhgpXW2_6GhmynOSRTpAbjKv-RZfAI71I08U</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9d56cd800047f48e877548dc48901a2e5332f7","tid":90307