00Z","msg":"而家又唔係香港人有份選<br />\n講咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e3df8443acf6c213a6bc8892cde2dce0c19a5e","tid":903074,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"國民黨班撚樣講上癮<br />\n又老又窮個唔停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a399f76cbd26ef5e16d1f3bb877344a4bc9a9308","tid":903074,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"明明藍營先最睇唔起香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15d063a45a4e00a27b8aaac99f5822c767e6b11","tid":903074,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"是但啦 wfc"},{"pid":"e810b91d6f41046b2e2cd22514f39b4da42dd28d","tid":903074,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"日本「森紀念財團」都市戰略研究所周四（18日）發表2018年全球城市綜合實力排名（Global Power City Index，GPCI），前3名仍是倫敦、紐約、東京，香港則留守第9位。<br />\n<br />\nGPCI在全球各地選擇44個主要城市，根據6大範疇、70個量度標準，計算排名結果，從而得出每個城市對全球「吸引力」程度。該6大範疇包括經濟、研究開發、文化交流、宜居性、環境及交通可達度。<br />\n<br />\n今年<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>排名前10</strong></span>的城市依序為倫敦、紐約、東京、巴黎、<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡</span>、阿姆斯特丹、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>首爾</strong></span>、柏林、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港</strong></span>和悉尼。北京和上海分別是第23名和第26名。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>台北</strong></span>則較去年的第36名進步一名，為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第35名</strong></span>。"}]}